RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT b.Customer_No,b.Customer_Name1 FROM Oltms_Customer b WHERE b.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND b.Record_Stat = 'O' ORDER BY Customer_Name1

SELECT DISTINCT Ticket_Id FROM Oltbs_Contract a, Tltb_Contract_Master b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No AND a.Latest_Version_No = b.Version_No AND a.Module_Code = 'TL' AND Nvl(b.Internal_Trade, 'N') <> 'Y' AND b.Branch LIKE Global.Current_Branch

SELECT B.Ticket_Id, B.Contract_Ref_No FROM oltbs_contract a, Tltbs_Contract_Master b WHERE A.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No AND B.Ticket_Id = ? AND b.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Tltbs_Contract_Master z WHERE z.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No) AND b.Counterparty = ? AND B.Contract_Ref_No NOT IN (SELECT Trade_Reference_No FROM Tltb_Ticket_Assignment_Fee WHERE Ticket_Id = ?) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Tltbs_Contract_Fee_Master c WHERE c.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No AND Tlpks_Fee_Services.Fn_Get_Fee_Type(sypks_utils.get_product(B.CONTRACT_REF_NO), c.Component) = 'AS' AND Event_Seq_No = (SELECT MAX(Event_Seq_No) FROM Tltbs_Contract_Fee_Master v WHERE v.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No AND v.Component = c.Component) AND c.Waiver = 'Y')
SELECT Ccy_Code, Ccy_Name FROM Cytms_Ccy_Defn WHERE Ccy_Code NOT IN (SELECT Currency FROM Tltbs_Ticket_Assignment_Fee WHERE Ticket_Id = ? AND Counterparty = ?)

SELECT DISTINCT a.Counterparty FROM Tltb_Contract_Master a, Oltbs_Contract b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = b.Contract_Ref_No AND a.Version_No = b.Latest_Version_No AND b.Contract_Status = 'A' AND Ticket_Id = ? AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM TLtbs_Contract_Fee_Master c WHERE c.Contract_Ref_No IN (SELECT Contract_Ref_No FROM Tltb_Contract_Master WHERE Ticket_Id = ? AND Counterparty = a.Counterparty) AND c.Fee_Type = 'AS' AND Event_Seq_No = (SELECT MAX(Event_Seq_No) FROM Tltbs_Contract_Fee_Master v WHERE v.Contract_Ref_No IN (SELECT Contract_Ref_No FROM Tltb_Contract_Master WHERE Ticket_Id = ? AND Counterparty = a.Counterparty) AND v.Component = c.Component) AND c.Waiver = 'N')

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(TICKET_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN order by ccy_code
SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, CURRENCY, COUNTERPARTY, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO, MODULE FROM OLTMS_INSTR WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
